<section xml:id="section-textbook">
    <title>Textbook</title>

    <p>
        We are using a new <em>free</em> textbook written by PCC faculty.
        The book is called <pubtitle>ORCCA (Open Resources for Community College Algebra)</pubtitle>.
    </p>

    <p>
        Access this book as a free
        <url href="http://spot.pcc.edu/math/orcca/ed2/html/" visual="spot.pcc.edu/math/orcca/ed2/html">web site</url>,
        as a (color or black-and-white)
        <url href="http://spot.pcc.edu/math/orcca/ed2/pdf/" visual="spot.pcc.edu/math/orcca/ed2/pdf">PDF</url>,
        for purchase from the
        <url href="https://bookstore.pcc.edu/store2/SelectTermDept.aspx" visual="bookstore.pcc.edu/store2/SelectTermDept.aspx">PCC book store</url> for $15.40, or for purchase from
        <url href="https://amzn.to/2Zo1wOZ" visual="amzn.to/2Zo1wOZ">Amazon</url> for $15.40.
    </p>

    <p>
        At <url href="pcc.edu/orcca"/>, there are many ORCCA-related resources,
        including a PDF document with the answers to odd-numbered exercises from the print copy.
    </p>

</section>
